text: is a former Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Hara was born on August 18, 1988. On March 29, 2005, when she was 16 years old, she debuted for the Japan national team against Australia. In April, she was selected by the Japan U-17 national team for the AFC U-17 Championship and Japan won the champions. ==Statistics== Japan Football Association Japan national team Year Apps Goals 2005 1 0 Total 1 0 ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese footballers Category:Japan women's international footballers
